author: Russell Brand
description:
Download the Allio App from the App Store / Google Play, or text “RUSSELL” to 511511. Investing involves risks. Including the potential loss of principal. Past performance does not guarantee results. See terms and conditions. 

Charlie Kirk’s assassination has become another battleground — the left branding him a fascist, the right using his death as proof of persecution. But beneath the noise lies a darker truth: when political opponents are dehumanized, violence becomes normalized. Online rhetoric radicalizes just like porn distorts intimacy, creating a culture where outrage replaces dialogue. The test now isn’t how loudly we condemn, but whether we can resist being pulled deeper into polarization — choosing compassion over control, forgiveness over exploitation.
